<h2 id="course-information">Course Information</h2>
<p>The basic principles of wireless communication are provided and multiple different applications of wireless communication system and mobile networks are introduced, including cellular networks, mobile IP, wireless LAN, satellite systems, ad-hoc networks, sensor networks, wireless PAN, etc.</p>

<h2 id="student-work">Student Work</h2>
<p>We collect and sort out all the homework from 2008 to now. Ten years accumulation, ten years precipitation. Many student achievements have been published in internationally renowned journals and conferences. We are committed to the combination of teaching and practice, and always stand in the forefront of the field.</p>

